data.description:
NEWLY REMODELED WITH NO HOA!!! This modern 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom LARGE cul-de-sac lot in Tempe has been beautifully renovated inside and out. Upon arrival notice the private courtyard and great curb appeal with fresh exterior paint. This charming home has new vinyl flooring and tile throughout. The inviting and open floor plan is perfect for entertaining with natural light, new ceiling fans, new interior paint and upgraded lighting. The open and spacious family room flows into the chef's kitchen featuring a gas range and stainless-steel appliances. The kitchen boasts designer shaker kitchen cabinets, stunning quartz countertops, new RO system, upgraded hardware, soft-close cabinets, new kitchen faucet, new garbage disposal and also features a butler's pantry with a drink fridge. The wood paneled breakfast bar in the kitchen is in the heart of the home which makes this a great space to cook and gather! The primary suite has a set of two contemporary sliding closet doors providing ample storage. Enter the ensuite which offers a newly tiled walk-in shower, renewed mirror and upgraded vanity. The secondary bedrooms have new interior doors, built-in dressers and a guest bathroom across the hall that has also been renovated with new tile, a mirror, upgraded vanity and shower/tub combo. The FLEX/bonus room makes for a great workspace/game room/playroom/ or can be  converted to a 4th bedroom - there are lots of options to utilize this space! It has direct backyard access through a new sliding glass door. The backyard is freshly landscaped, ready to install winter grass (automatic timer sprinklers installed), with new rocks, plants and citrus trees. There is an RV Gate for backyard entry. A gas stub  already installed for a future BBQ or fireplace absolutely perfect for outdoor entertaining and Arizona sunsets.
Additional upgrades include new wiring with a new main breaker box, a new roof, a new AC and all new duct work, new PEX plumbing, new gas water heater, new baseboards, stainless steel washer and dryer and garage has been pre-wired for electric vehicle charging! Centrally located to the Loop 101 and US 60, close to ASU, Mesa Community College, EVIT, Sky Harbor, shopping, and restaurants.
